                </li>
                <li>
                  <button class="button" type="submit" name="reserve" id="reserve">Reserve</button>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </form>

            <aside class="note">
              <p>* As a reminder, our seating is limited, please be accurate. Any guests who have not RSVP’ed by [date] will not be allowed to attend. If you have concerns/questions, please <a href="#">contact us</a> as soon as possible.</p>
